+        Args:
+            router_logits: Router logits tensor (for TRTLLMGen backend)
+            do_finalize: Whether to finalize output (for TRTLLMGen backend)
+            all_rank_num_tokens: Token counts per rank (for TRTLLMGen backend moe_output)
